{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8e1c7740d6","title":"准备粉碎正面之敌及侧面登陆之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f6bec06727","index":0,"year":1951,"month":6,"day":4,"articleId":"8e1c7740d6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"42a69fd185","type":"title","text":"准备粉碎正面之敌及侧面登陆之敌","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e1c7740d6"},{"id":"26de8c188f","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e1c7740d6"},{"id":"6b6c10fce0","type":"paragraph","text":"据国民党方面五月三十一日东京情报称“联军将从东线向西北推进。自元山起，至开城止一斜线，压追共军撤至平之北。可能另组元山登陆部队，以促成共军提早放弃临津江以东地区”等语。此种阴谋应肯定是真实的。我全军应振奋精神，加速准备，粉碎正面之敌及从侧面登陆之敌。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e1c7740d6"},{"id":"27120d06e0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e1c7740d6"},{"id":"4be36c0ccf","type":"paragraph","text":"六月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e1c7740d6"},{"id":"c41646ba33","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]德怀，即彭德怀，当时任中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e1c7740d6"}],"page":{"id":"08718b56b2","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e1c7740d6","start":365,"end":365}}}},"__N_SSG":true}